4.40	The_Return_of_the_Black_Widowers	The Return of the Black Widowers	The Return of the Black Widowers is a collection of mystery short stories by science fiction author Isaac Asimov featuring his fictional club of mystery solvers, the Black Widowers. It was first published in hardcover by Carroll &amp; Graf in November 2003.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/8/86/Return_of_the_Black_Widowers_cover.jpg
